"春之森林","iso_3166_1":"CN"},{"type":"","title":"思春の森","iso_3166_1":"JP"},{"type":"judul alternatif","title":"Cinta monyet","iso_3166_1":"ID"},{"type":"","title":"春的森林","iso_3166_1":"CN"},{"type":"","title":"思春的森林","iso_3166_1":"CN"}],"videos":[],"watch_providers":{"results":{}},"wikidata_id":"Q566406","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-26T00:26:13.98645+00:00","region":null,"main_poster":null,"images":{"logos":[{"width":898,"height":235,"file_path":"/q2zJqNmDhWoBV8PA3Q32HB0ByI1.png","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":3.821,"vote_average":0}],"posters":[{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/nu5uj47KSF73VPEiIRYdPLJ96j7.jpg","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/9kDVSW5zK1FV02ABe7G7ZvbwuBM.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1000,"height":1500,"file_path":"/f1RFRmPnPdFNcQd1ez0ifiU93u2.jpg","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":500,"height":750,"file_path":"/prAbJSVBQepa1XmiRvM4K4TIPca.jpg","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","vote_count":3,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":500,"height":750,"file_path":"/wJjtS6NoxgbO8Z4Ba2aX2J01anV.jpg","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0},{"width":1200,"height":1800,"file_path":"/pMDKCczpXdWUTqeOAjfvamrY97H.jpg","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/2AI3pSt5sbAEav6isVDIeCuiZql.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/caM4j0JHCMDBdd47KMDJUB663l7.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/lhbBsep1nnBNWjUiBFWKol9JtDX.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/3kfRu1CjAZSnkuKloAe7gcvDIxB.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3680,"height":2070,"file_path":"/qeVTw1svczuExFLqSHLJeDhtUKN.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/n2vDijWsVtYi4yki0rMEtmKCd3V.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/8vvLeQGn2BOcvAEkbKYcML11rpK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/xI9ueCS29r7w2qVkP8Yw1AK9m0F.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T02:47:53.898+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Playing with Love","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Laura and Fabrizio have been meeting every summer in the forest by her parent's summer home. Fabrizio is a solitary boy with only his dog for company; Laura a sweet but unconfident child. This summer new aspects enter into their story as both are growing up. Laura is falling in love with Fabrizio, while he displays a new sexual awareness of her masked by his malice. Things develop further when they meet Sylvia who, unlike the innocent Laura, is confident and assertive. Fabrizio develops a fascination with her, eventually bribing Laura to fetch her to the forest to join them in play."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Spielen wir Liebe","runtime":94,"tagline":"Sie lieben und sie quälen sich!","homepage":"","overview":"Laura (12) und Fabrizio (14) haben sich bereits in den Sommerferien des Vorjahres immer wieder im Wald getroffen. Laura bemerkt nun allerdings, dass sich in ihrer Beziehung etwas verändert hat: Aus den kindlichen Spielen der Vergangenheit ist etwas ganz Neues entstanden, das schon bald zu einer sklavischen Hingabe von Laura an Fabrizio führt. Dieser beginnt Laura mit teilweise drastischen Methoden zu quälen. Trotzdem kommt Laura immer wieder zu Fabrizio zurück. Schließlich führt die Neugierde beider zu ihren ersten sexuellen Kontakten untereinander."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Распутное детство","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Лес, его таинственными местами: развалинами, пещерами, водопадом, озером, становится местом постоянных встреч 12-летний Лауры с несколько чудаковатым мальчиком Фабрицио, который испытывает серьезные проблемы кризиса переходного возраста. Первая близость, и ей кажется, что она самая счастливая на белом свете и их совместное счастье неразрушимо. Однако любовь, подчеркнутая сексом, приносит плоды проблем и изрядную долю разочарования.  Мальчик, в буквальном смысле слова, начинает измываться над несчастной Лаурой, над ее привязанностью и ее чувствами. Он демонстративно унижает ее. Игра принимает жесткий и даже жестокий характер. Лаура оказывается поставлена в положение рабыни, безмерно любящей своего повелителя. И в этом спектакле Фабрицио активно подыгрывает Сильвия, столь же юная как и Лаура, но более дерзкая и нахальная. Обеим девушкам нравится Фабрицио. Напряженность между тремя персонажами любовного треугольника возрастает и достигнув пика — разрывается трагедией."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Maladolescenza","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Een tienerjongen en -meisje zijn op seksueel gebied aan het verkennen. Het gaat mis wanneer een ander meisje op het toneel verschijnt. De jongen raakt verleid door deze jongedame, waardoor de andere genegeerd wordt. De spanning tussen de drie loopt op..."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Jeux interdits de l'adolescence","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Trois adolescents Fabrizio, Laura et Silvia, seuls dans une forêt, se livrent à des jeux érotiques."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Casal de adolescentes vive em local paradisíaco momentos de intensa felicidade e descobertas amorosas e sexuais, até que uma nova amiga surge para confundir e desestruturar a relação entre os dois."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"春的森林","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　在西德一片美丽古老的森林中，隐居这一对神仙眷侣般的小夫妻——法布里兹奥（Martin Loeb 马丁•劳伯 饰）和劳拉（Lara Wendel 拉拉•温德尔 饰）。他们俩在此优哉游哉，好不快活。  　　少女希尔维娅（Eva Ionesco 伊娃•爱洛尼斯科 饰）假期回到了森林附近的古堡家中，她在林中邂逅了法布里兹奥，两人迅速陷入热恋。他们的关系引起了劳拉的注意，三人在这感情的漩涡中逐渐失去了控制……  　　本片是意大利女导演穆尔吉亚（Pier Giuseppe Murgia）的第一部电影作品，影片因展现了少年性爱而被禁长达20年，1999年影片解冻后由日本购买版权，发行了精装版VHS。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"3 genç bulundukları yaz tatilinde hayatlarını tümden değiştirecek deneyimlere tanık olurlar"},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Serdülőkori játékok","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Laura a nyári szünetben megismerkedik a 14 éves Fabrizio-val, aki farkaskutyájával egész nap az erdőben bolyong. A két kamaszlány felfedez egy barlangot, ahol egy fiú elcsábítja Laurát, de rövid idő elteltével egyre agresszívebben bánik a lánnyal. A helyzet tovább romlik, amikor megismerkednek Sylviával. Sylvia, Laurával ellentétben egyáltalán nem naiv, ráadásul szexuális téren is elég tapasztalt és kegyetlenkedésben, erőszakosságban még Fabrizio-val is felveszi a versenyt. Hármójuk erőszakos és cseppet sem ártatlan játszadozása, feltartózhatatlanul közeledik a tragikus végkifejlet felé."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Maladolescencia","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Laura y Fabrizio, una pareja de adolescentes, pasan el verano en la casa de verano familiar de uno de ellos. Juntos pasan el día en el bosque de los alrededores, disfrutando de la naturaleza y amándose. Pero la irrupción de Silvia provoca en Fabrizio un cambio de actitud en su relación con Laura."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Розпусне дитинство","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Лаура і Фабріціо зустрічалися щоліта в лісі в літньому будиночку її батьків. Фабріціо — 14-річний хлопець-одинак, компанію якому складала лише його собака; Лаура — 11-літня мила, але не впевнена в собі дитина, від її особи ведеться розповідь у фільмі."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"유년의 사랑","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《유년의 사랑》은 이탈리아에서 제작된 피에르 쥬세페 무르기아 감독의 1977년 드라마, 멜로/로맨스 영화이다. 라라 웬델 등이 주연으로 출연하였다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"春之森林","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在西德一片美麗古老的森林中，隱居這一對神仙眷侶般的小夫妻——法布里茲奧（Martin Loeb 馬丁•勞伯飾）和勞拉（Lara Wendel 拉拉•溫德爾飾） 。他們倆在此優哉游哉，好不快活。\r 　　少女希爾維婭（Eva Ionesco 伊娃•愛洛尼斯科 飾）假期回到了森林附近的古堡家中，她在林中邂逅了法布里茲奧，兩人迅速陷入熱戀。他們的關係引起了勞拉的注意，三人在這感情的漩渦中逐漸失去了控制……\r 本片是意大利女導演穆爾吉亞（Pier Giuseppe Murgia）的第一部電影作品，影片因展現了少年性愛而被禁長達20年，1999年影片解凍後由日本購買版權，發行了精裝版VHS。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um adolescente cresce brincando e brigando com seu cão pastor alemão e fazendo jogos de adultos com duas igualmente jovens meninas  em uma floresta de sonho que, eventualmente, fica estranha e sombria."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Fin dall'infanzia, Fabrizio e Laura si godono insieme le vacanze estive nel loro luogo preferito, in una foresta della Boemia che Fabrizio considera come il proprio regno. Quest'estate però Fabrizio e Laura sono cresciuti e non sono più gli stessi spensierati bambini di un tempo, ma due adolescenti alle prese con i primi turbamenti del sesso."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Maladolescenza","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Laura (Lara Wendel) od lat wakacje spędza wraz z rodzicami na prowincji w domu położonymobok lasu. Okres letni zawsze upływa jej na zabawach z rówieśnikiem Fabrizio (Martin Loeb). Tego roku Laura odkrywa że w zachowaniu i zwyczajach chłopca nastąpiły znaczące zmiany. Fabrizio nabywa skłonności do nieuzasadnionego okrucieństwa, jest władczy i wymaga od dziewczynki całkowitego posłuszeństwa. Wykorzystuje uczucie jakim ona go obdarza i skłania do kontaktów seksualnych. Wkrótce do owej sytuacji wkroczy postać pewnej siebie Silvii (Eva Ionesco), która zajmie pozycję towarzyszki Fabrizia. Od tej pory nieśmiała i zamknięta w sobie Laura coraz częściej pada ofiarą bezlitosnych gier dwójki swych towarzyszy."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"思春の森","runtime":0,"tagline":"思春の森は危険な恋","homepage":"","overview":"少女ラウラは毎夏、避暑ですごす山村で一人の少年を遊び友達に、王と王妃を気取るのだが、その年は少年の様子が違う。明らかに性的好奇の目が注がれ、態度も横暴。悩む少女に少年は、森の外れの別荘に暮らす少女シルヴィアを仲間に誘うよう命令する。そして、その娘が王女として君臨。美しいカップルを前に奴隷のように屈従するしかないラウラ。しかし、シルヴィアの高慢さは少年にも手に負えないものだった…。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Bermain dengan Cinta","runtime":94,"tagline":"Hutan masa muda adalah cinta yang berbahaya","homepage":"","overview":"Laura dan Fabrizio bertemu setiap musim panas di hutan dekat rumah musim panas orang tuanya. Fabrizio adalah seorang anak laki-laki penyendiri yang hanya ditemani oleh anjingnya; Laura anak yang manis tapi tidak percaya diri. Musim panas ini, aspek-aspek baru masuk ke dalam kisah mereka seiring keduanya tumbuh dewasa. Laura jatuh cinta dengan Fabrizio, sementara dia menunjukkan kesadaran seksual baru tentang Fabrizio yang ditutupi oleh kebenciannya. Segalanya berkembang lebih jauh ketika mereka bertemu Sylvia yang, tidak seperti Laura yang lugu, percaya diri dan tegas. Fabrizio mulai tertarik padanya, akhirnya menyuap Laura untuk menjemputnya ke hutan untuk bergabung dengan mereka bermain."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"春之森林","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在西德一片美麗古老的森林中，隱居這一對神仙眷侶般的小夫妻——法布里茲奧（Martin Loeb 馬丁•勞伯飾）和勞拉（Lara Wendel 拉拉•温德爾飾） 。他們倆在此優哉遊哉，好不快活。  少女希爾維婭（Eva Ionesco 伊娃•愛洛尼斯科 飾）假期回到了森林附近的古堡家中，她在林中邂逅了法布里茲奧，兩人迅速陷入熱戀。他們的關係引起了勞拉的注意，三人在這感情的漩渦中逐漸失去了控制…… 本片是義大利女導演穆爾吉亞（Pier Giuseppe Murgia）的第一部電影作品，影片因展現了少年性愛而被禁長達 20 年，1999 年影片解凍後由日本購買版權，發行了精裝版 VHS。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":46581,"adult":false,"title":"Immoral Tales","video":false,"overview":"Four erotic tales from in various historical eras. The first, 'The Tide', is set in the present day, and concerns a student and his young female cousin stranded on the beach by the tide, secluded from prying eyes. 'Therese Philosophe' is set in the nineteenth century, and concerns a girl being locked in her bedroom, where she contemplates the erotic potential of the objects contained within it. 'Erzsebet Bathory' is a portrait of the sixteenth-century countess who allegedly bathed in the blood of virgins, while 'Lucrezia Borgia' concerns an incestuous fifteenth-century orgy involving Lucrezia, her brother, and her father the Pope.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.1511,"vote_count":271,"poster_path":"/dFPQD3e5uonv7bKTYsi7TqtKxYx.jpg","release_date":"1974-08-28","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/lv7bRurrhBo3vjcwJNztb2ZkDu9.jpg","original_title":"Contes immoraux","original_language":"fr"},{"id":62564,"adult":false,"title":"Turn Me On, Dammit!","video":false,"overview":"In Skoddeheimen, Norway, 15-year-old Alma is consumed by her hormones and fantasies that range from sweetly romantic images of Artur, the boyfriend she yearns for, to daydreams about practically everybody she lays eyes on.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5066,"vote_count":223,"poster_path":"/weBjKfREQrbexrKh2oMQ9PWbch2.jpg","release_date":"2011-08-19","vote_average":6.339,"backdrop_path":"/5S3QuLiPOZs1PPwcusuSTiCSaRN.jpg","original_title":"Få meg på, for faen","original_language":"no"},{"id":35862,"adult":false,"title":"Wedding Trough","video":false,"overview":"Alone on a farm, a man spends his days tending to his animals, with a particular love for his sow. After an illicit encounter between the two creatures, the pig gives birth. However, tragedy strikes when the man tries to force the newborn piglets to love him as he loves them.","genre_ids":[27,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2339,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/xYO7GWQjVOuPxjtmVGR6MZx6YNG.jpg","release_date":"1975-10-01","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/qxocP27gvQ1tJEwD5saIsEHhR4b.jpg","original_title":"Vase de Noces","original_language":"fr"},{"id":458780,"adult":false,"title":"Ballads","video":false,"overview":"The story of a young man who tragically lost his lover in a horriffic motorcycle accident. Now working at a video store and selling uncensored gay hardcore pornography under the counter, he one day discovers the worlds most bizarre snuff video... which happens to \"star\" a man who looks exactly like his dead lover. Pushed over the edge by this event, the protagonist goes on a violent rampage, attempting to murder everybody involved in the video's creation.","genre_ids":[18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2075,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/uw7LukgXcR8jIbXz9riurgvTJTk.jpg","release_date":"1993-04-29","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/kBFJ1T7RhVtjCYrQDOMoKPOKvc5.jpg","original_title":"バラードに抱かれて","original_language":"ja"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.7563,"vote_count":11389,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0422,"vote_count":27339,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.6244,"vote_count":25460,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":105,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future","video":false,"overview":"Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.5525,"vote_count":21421,"poster_path":"/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg","release_date":"1985-07-03","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/qskzmLTbarKnXDbo2HRj4NJ3vcW.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future","original_language":"en"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.721,"vote_count":14579,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.423,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.4976,"vote_count":26828,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.903,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":299534,"adult":false,"title":"Avengers: Endgame","video":false,"overview":"After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War, the universe is in ruins due to the efforts of the Mad Titan, Thanos. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers must assemble once more in order to undo Thanos' actions and restore order to the universe once and for all, no matter what consequences may be in store.","genre_ids":[12,878,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0537,"vote_count":27295,"poster_path":"/ulzhLuWrPK07P1YkdWQLZnQh1JL.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-24","vote_average":8.236,"backdrop_path":"/7RyHsO4yDXtBv1zUU3mTpHeQ0d5.jpg","original_title":"Avengers: Endgame","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7588,"vote_count":14042,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":272,"adult":false,"title":"Batman Begins","video":false,"overview":"Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.","genre_ids":[18,80,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.5976,"vote_count":22282,"poster_path":"/sPX89Td70IDDjVr85jdSBb4rWGr.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-10","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/9IIBboV7MCT0bTxzXHmWK1Hq558.jpg","original_title":"Batman Begins","original_language":"en"},{"id":468224,"adult":false,"title":"Tolkien","video":false,"overview":"England, early 20th century. The future writer and philologist John Ronald Reuel Tolkien (1892-1973) and three of his schoolmates create a strong bond between them as they share the same passion for literature and art, a true fellowship that strengthens as they grow up, but the outbreak of World War I threatens to shatter it.","genre_ids":[10752,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3956,"vote_count":1516,"poster_path":"/A7eYO3t7oZQdfJj5KlJBI7GhT9H.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-03","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/4HXiEsWUEMzJNFwjJv6oUaocqJU.jpg","original_title":"Tolkien","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":14,"adult":false,"title":"American Beauty","video":false,"overview":"Lester Burnham, a depressed suburban father in a mid-life crisis, decides to turn his hectic life around after developing an infatuation with his daughter's attractive friend.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.4774,"vote_count":12827,"poster_path":"/wby9315QzVKdW9BonAefg8jGTTb.jpg","release_date":"1999-09-15","vote_average":8.002,"backdrop_path":"/2ndw55F40IkALzWyjCCza3M6nqM.jpg","original_title":"American Beauty","original_language":"en"},{"id":13510,"adult":false,"title":"Eden Lake","video":false,"overview":"When a young couple goes to a remote wooded lake for a romantic getaway, their quiet weekend is shattered by an aggressive group of local kids. Rowdiness quickly turns to rage as the teens terrorize the couple in unimaginable ways, and a weekend outing becomes a bloody battle for survival.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.608,"vote_count":2024,"poster_path":"/tOg6ElTe1mJwaCFN0172U4oso22.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-12","vote_average":6.832,"backdrop_path":"/s9v1QZMVhwShQ7415jPhtfqzyjG.jpg","original_title":"Eden Lake","original_language":"en"},{"id":84892,"adult":false,"title":"The Perks of Being a Wallflower","video":false,"overview":"Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, 1991. High school freshman Charlie is a wallflower, always watching life from the sidelines, until two senior students, Sam and her stepbrother Patrick, become his mentors, helping him discover the joys of friendship, music and love.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.7679,"vote_count":11037,"poster_path":"/aKCvdFFF5n80P2VdS7d8YBwbCjh.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-20","vote_average":7.803,"backdrop_path":"/aM6E4DBP6588q3tEr9hz41ls80q.jpg","original_title":"The Perks of Being a Wallflower","original_language":"en"},{"id":527774,"adult":false,"title":"Raya and the Last Dragon","video":false,"overview":"Long ago, in the fantasy world of Kumandra, humans and dragons lived together in harmony. But when an evil force threatened the land, the dragons sacrificed themselves to save humanity. Now, 500 years later, that same evil has returned and it’s up to a lone warrior, Raya, to track down the legendary last dragon to restore the fractured land and its divided people.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,28,12],"media_