nd where she finally finds true self-acceptance.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3557,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/acyQiLOzCyA3LTU4xA4g3YiSFik.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-22","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/xhh8Q7uG7mA7gsHJdn6xEzrBScm.jpg","original_title":"Vaselinetjie","original_language":"af"},{"id":467199,"adult":false,"title":"Method","video":false,"overview":"A seasoned actor and a pop star are cast as leads in a gay romantic play. As the actor teaches the pop star method acting, the line between fiction and reality is blurred and they become drawn to each other.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.5383,"vote_count":57,"poster_path":"/5hh1gM0YUqzIjqSWCGzGMFt2fo0.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-02","vote_average":6.886,"backdrop_path":"/yY13YA1nKm46ORAZQ6zKkjE8Gdg.jpg","original_title":"메소드","original_language":"ko"},{"id":3170,"adult":false,"title":"Bambi","video":false,"overview":"Bambi's tale unfolds from season to season as the young prince of the forest learns about life, love, and friends.","genre_ids":[16,18,10751],"popularity":5.0868,"vote_count":5953,"poster_path":"/wV9e2y4myJ4KMFsyFfWYcUOawyK.jpg","release_date":"1942-08-14","vote_average":7.008,"backdrop_path":"/1ZKHzSGJm0kvlCp4echAOtKnDTm.jpg","original_title":"Bambi","original_language":"en"},{"id":6537,"adult":false,"title":"The Orphanage","video":false,"overview":"A woman brings her family back to her childhood home, which used to be an orphanage, intent on reopening it. Before long, her son starts to communicate with a new invisible friend.","genre_ids":[27,18,53],"popularity":1.9388,"vote_count":3066,"poster_path":"/vIpi1KtHLXUOfSVC2m6MqpjSPgL.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-20","vote_average":7.23,"backdrop_path":"/g6pNnKmvTkNlEvn0ScwstYvhFE.jpg","original_title":"El orfanato","original_language":"es"},{"id":470092,"adult":false,"title":"Nothing","video":false,"overview":"Bia just turned eighteen. The end of the year is coming and also the ACTs. People at school and Bia’s parents are pre