ty, who tries to convince him to drown his wife.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.9136,"vote_count":880,"poster_path":"/oj8ZW8jKXBSs8F1e5iWsTUeXSJW.jpg","release_date":"1927-11-04","vote_average":7.818,"backdrop_path":"/hKrrCigPFmhv1bg5IJl9nzjEaN4.jpg","original_title":"Sunrise: A Song of Two Humans","original_language":"en"},{"id":409,"adult":false,"title":"The English Patient","video":false,"overview":"In the 1930s, Count Almásy is a Hungarian map maker employed by the Royal Geographical Society to chart the vast expanses of the Sahara Desert along with several other prominent explorers. As World War II unfolds, Almásy enters into a world of love, betrayal, and politics.","genre_ids":[18,10749,10752],"popularity":4.4471,"vote_count":2342,"poster_path":"/8eHHqMg8qEYtVw8LQLygsHXSR2q.jpg","release_date":"1996-11-14","vote_average":7.155,"backdrop_path":"/em5kAUF8QbwThG5BCqVgFomxNT5.jpg","original_title":"The English Patient","original_language":"en"},{"id":428,"adult":false,"title":"Summer '04","video":false,"overview":"A character study of a family on vacation. The emotional abyss and problems are behind the seemingly nice facade of an intact family as they experience guilt, love, and jealousy.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.4413,"vote_count":25,"poster_path":"/iXZX1B2BaAXEo59KCV1CY4K1S4j.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-11","vote_average":5.66,"backdrop_path":"/sycZVq9EFigchg6QEyCHzjrcHIf.jpg","original_title":"Sommer '04","original_language":"de"},{"id":547,"adult":false,"title":"The Horse Whisperer","video":false,"overview":"The mother of a severely traumatized daughter enlists the aid of a unique horse trainer to help the girl's equally injured horse.","genre_ids":[12,18,10749],"popularity":2.9415,"vote_count":1181,"poster_path":"/ptkDeHY2mRJVyNRyxb9TgyAjTYs.jpg","release_date":"1998-02-01","vote_average":6.891,"backdrop_path":"/ww9pokP6M6gp2Iu0o3sT5B7eN66.jpg","original_title":"The Horse Whisperer","original_language":"en"},{"id":554,"adult":false,"title":"The Cuckoo","video":false,"overview":"September of 1944, a few days before Finland went out of the Second World War. A chained to a rock Finnish sniper-kamikadze Veikko managed to set himself free. Ivan, a captain of the Soviet Army, arrested by the Front Secret Police 'Smersh', has a narrow escape. They are soldiers of the two enemy armies. A Lapp woman Anni gives a shelter to both of them at her farm. For Anni they are not enemies, but just men.","genre_ids":[18,10749,35],"popularity":1.1526,"vote_count":116,"poster_path":"/g0bVxxdeAkDwzLoJq7o8ehQZWa6.jpg","release_date":"2002-09-12","vote_average":7.06,"backdrop_path":"/fvpvcIY2yYYO8FKc3IGfwrNSzMH.jpg","original_title":"Кукушка","original_language":"ru"},{"id":1059518,"adult":false,"title":"Amizade Inesperada","video":false,"overview":"Luiz is a high school student who, by neglecting his studies, gets a failing grade. To help him, the teacher gives Toni the mission to teach the student the unlearned material. However, Luiz has a history of school violence against Toni. Putting aside the past the two accept the challenge given by the teacher and end up living an unpretentious romance.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35,10770],"popularity":0.2177,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/hS3xmolrqlg9MPlUM6IEyU3fsMy.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-21","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/wSHTEhAzVmRRpR72k4qVv0Nyc8o.jpg","original_title":"Amizade Inesperada","original_language":"pt"},{"id":441,"adult":false,"title":"Human Nature","video":false,"overview":"Obsessive scientist Nathan and his lover, the naturalist Lila, discover Puff: a man born and raised in the wild. As Nathan trains the wild man in the civilized ways of the world, Lila fights to preserve the man’s natural state. In the power struggle that ensues, an unusual love triangle emerges.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.6807,"vote_count":284,"poster_path":"/8FlxH4q1plGzdoJmK2VHgap3Ly7.jpg","release_date":"2001-09-12","vote_average":6.007,"backdrop_path":"/kz0xtrWKisCEOPB2qdiSWOUigkd.jpg","original_title":"Human Nature","original_language":"en"},{"id":3565,"adult":false,"title":"Underground","video":false,"overview":"A working-class love story set in and around the London Underground of the 1920s. Two men – gentle Bill and brash Bert – meet and are attracted to the same woman on the same day at the same Underground station. But the lady chooses Bill, and Bert isn't the type to take rejection lightly...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.2313,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/6RK3O2MMvu7bJWpnauwJDyDDaoO.jpg","release_date":"1928-07-01","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/ybzkQYyY2Ulcn8wtfLsVXoeDqFh.jpg","original_title":"Underground","original_language":"en"},{"id":3682,"adult":false,"title":"54","video":false,"overview":"When the mastermind behind New York's infamous Studio 54 disco plucks young Shane from the sea of faces clamoring to get inside his club, he not only gets his foot in the door, but lands a coveted job behind the bar — and a front-row ticket to the most legendary party on the planet!","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":1.5382,"vote_count":509,"poster_path":"/gLjt54vow8CEOHdgRkQCyXwbq52.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-28","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":"/rGaXfUvsnIK32RikoCnYKoYsQNc.jpg","original_title":"54","original_language":"en"},{"id":274817,"adult":false,"title":"Wood Job!","video":false,"overview":"After failing his university entrance exam, Yuki Hirano sets his eyes on the role of a forestry trainee. Setting off for training he doubts his decision many times, but eventually after passing the training course, he is sent to Kamusari Village for a year of work experience - where he becomes assimilated with the beauty of nature and the warm-hearted people of the village.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.7153,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/gvo0367R3pWJJrwGDRMMOCZnSwY.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-10","vote_average":7.388,"backdrop_path":"/zXMd5VDsPK8v65BpiOSjxUqqiFs.jpg","original_title":"WOOD JOB! ～神去なあなあ日常～","original_language":"ja"},{"id":3538,"adult":false,"title":"Gisela","video":false,"overview":"Gisela is a young wife and mother, living in a working class German Housing Scheme. She is a supermarket cashier, her husband a delivery driver. The marriage is stale but together they are working their way up into the middle class.  George and Gisela evidently knew each other as teenagers. They live on the same scheme and George introduces her to his friend Paul. There is instant mutual attraction. Gisela spontaneously goes to a party that they invite her to that evening, where she and Paul begin a sexual relationship.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2873,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/8r0eSdUDlVuIl7jEi65TlvnmdDm.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-27","vote_average":4.55,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Gisela","original_language":"de"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0076749","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q566406","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"19096"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148613,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1977-06-23T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"18"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"es","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1979-09-04T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"18"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1977-05-17T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"18"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1977-05-17T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"US","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_da